description.narrative: Croatia Emergency Preparedness (Sisak Area). School Repairs/Refurbishment (Copan, Honduras). BiH Travel Expenses FY17/18. Honduras Disaster Relief Supplies (Foam Mattresses). Kveshi School Renovation by the Administrative Boundary Line. Dnipro Hospital for Veterans Renovation. Medgidia City Hospital Renovation. Raramuri Indigenous Kitchen. Hygiene Kits. MEDCAP - PUERTO BARRIOS. Support for The Bahamas Urban Renewal Center. Chilean SMEs HA/DR workshop. Rose Hall Medical Outreach (Region 6). Equipment for 'La Mansión' Children's Shelter. Community Health Emergency Rapid Response 2018. Purchase Equipment to Aid in Disaster Relief (Flooding) in Mayaro/Rio Claro Trinidad. Elizaveta Preschool Sanitation facilities renovation. Disaster Relief Supplies in Support of Cauca River flooding. Support to elementary School in Svljig. Semporna Water Village Pathway. Renovations in FECHAC Shelter Kitchens in Ciudad Juarez. Renovation of Svencionys Fire and Rescue Station. Cambodia Blood Product Safety Capacity Building. Agadez, Niger; Primary and Secondary School Desks. SMEE FF Conference and training for UHR and CONRED. Predictive Flooding Technical Exchange - Phase 2. Renovation of public secondary school in Kolasin. Santa Cruz Primary School SPMAGTF. Construction of Infrastructure for Emergency Medical Vehicles, Staff and Training Purposes at Imanta. NSW Turbo School Kits for Turbo, Antioquia. Neuquen EOC. Helipad Construction for Niksic General Hospital. Marqadah Desk and Chair Provision. Disaster Relief Warehouse # 4 Huehuetenango. CMSE Pasto - MEDCAP in Policarpa, Narino. Support to Nogales DIF Women's Affairs Office. Dubasarii Vechi Rural Medical Clinic Reconstruction. First responder PPE for UHR. School Kits. CAT 8363 - MEDCAP - Santa Ana. TTO SANGRE GRANDE DMU donation of 2 Rescue Boats. Fire Fighters Vehicle and Machinery Rescue PACE Phase V. Lima Fire Departments Equipment Donation. Prachin Buri Torch Outreach. CAT 8363- Centro Escolar Atonal, Barrio Cruz Galana, Izalco, Sonsonate. Disaster Preparedness COPECO's Warehouse. San Lorenzo, Valle. Winter Supplies for Ruwayshid Youth 2019. Al Ameen School. Casa Amiga Homeless Shelter Renovation. Klikach - Prolet Kindergarten Energy Efficiency Measures. Primary School 'Xhemail Kada' in Peja. African Partnership Outbreak Response Alliance V (APORA V) Conference FY18-1. School Paint Donation: 4 schools in Guatemala Department. Jadeed Bagara Obstetric/Gynecological/Pediatric Clinic Equipment. School Repairs/Refurbishment (Francisco Morazan, Honduras). Well Improvement Project-Tsakatalam-Niger. 2017 Library in a Box. OST Tumaco School Kits Barbacoas in support of JTF Hercules, TF Poseidon. Beit Chlala Generator Provision. VP Initiate-HAP Mgr-MEDCAP for Narino Barbacoas Phase I. Lviv Kindergarten Renovation for kids with special needs. CGFM, Binacional COL- , MEDCAP Tarapaca. AMAZONAS. Mexico CBRN Enterprise (UFR Request). Medical Engagement: Quimistan, Santa Barbara MEDCAP. MEDCAP - Champerico. U.S. Country Team Initiative, MEDCAP, Llorente, Health Event. MEDCAP - Chiquimula. Adapt DM Course Train the Trainer Course in English and French (Phase 4). Secondary School 'Adem Gllavica' in Lipjan. Croatian Maritime Rescue Coordination and Training Center. Neuquen Warehouse #1. TTO Couva/Tabaquite/Talparo DMU donation of 2 Rescue Boats. DRW WAREHOUSE OPERATONS Training & Equipment - Esquintla, Guatemala. USAR Re-supply for UEPCB Jalisco and ERUM Mexico City. Farkhor District School Supplies. Mansurah Health Clinic Supplies. Installation of Furniture & Equipment and EOC Management Training for Nevis. Strazhets- Center for Victims of Domestic Violence Renovation. MEDCAP - Genova, San Marcos. COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, School Desks for Riohacha, Institucion Educativa Almirante Padilla.. Rotoplas Water Storage Tanks. Manbij Substation Refurbishment. Renovation of the elementary school in Berane. Minnieh Ambulance Refurbishment. Construction of Administrative Wing at ODM - Dominica. CCDR USNORTHCOM 2018 TIP Shelter. MEDCAP, Igenieros, El Quiche. OST Tumaco, JTF Hercules and TF Poseidon MEDCAP Vereda Los Domingo- Charco, Narino. CGFM, Binacional COL-PAN, MEDCAP Acandi. CHOCO. Croatia Emergency Preparedness (Zagreb Area). COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, Classroom Refurbishment in Riohacha, Comunidad Juan de Aragon.. Croatia Emergency Preparedness (Osijek Area). Village Water Catchment and Wells. Argentine Navy Sponsored orphnage. Construction of EOC & DRW Facility at Castle Bruce, Dominica. Suwar (DaZ Province) School Supplies. EOD Level 1 Mission 1. CAT El Salvador- Medicamientos Comunidad Tierra Blanca, San Miguel. Regional Hospital Puerto Lempira Pediatric-Maternity Annex. OST Tumaco, TF Hercules and TF Poseidon MEDCAP Vereda Bajito Vaqueria, Tumaco. Fire Station in Belmopan. HA Renovation of Aluksne Fire Station, SFRS. USAR Re-supply for UEPCB Jalisco. Croatia Emergency Preparedness (Pula Area). Croatia Emergency Preparedness (Split Area). Repairs to Mexico Mammography Equipment. Training House for Firefighters. Novo Selo - Therapy Sector in Ivan Vazov Auxiliary School. CGFM-Tumaco, Narino. Yambol -NIkolay Petrini Middle School Bathrooms Renovation. Udon Thani Torch Outreach ICW Teak Torch. Primary School 'Dëshmorët e Kombit' in Baran, Peja. Consumable Supplies, Transportation, and Translation Expense in support of CRBs and Pilot Courses. TTO Tunapuna/Piarco DMU donation of 2 Rescue Boats. Multipurpose Facility, Centro Escolar Jose Napoleon Duarte, Apopa. National Public Health Laboratory Strengthening. School Renovation: Mirtha Torres School, San Pedro Sula, Cortes. Medical Engagement: Puerto Cortes Cortes MEDCAP. Purchase Equipment to Aid in Disaster Relief (Flooding) in Eastern Trinidad. CAT 8363 - MEDCAP - La Libertad. COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, School Kits for Riohacha, Institucion Educativa Denzil.. San Isidro Government School. NI - EOD LVL 1 Mission 2. Kinolhas Health Post - Addition for Bloodwork Laboratory. Busayra Clinic Equipment. Drinking Water and Sanitation System Repair. EOC and DRW (2 in 1) plus Helipad - Amazonas, Peru. Linden Medical Outreach. Construction of the building where the Kindergarten and Health Unit are located in Sheqishte, Patos.. School Renovation: CEB Luis Bogran-Tela, department of Atlantida. Siparia, Debe/Penal water retention ponds. SREBRENIK municipality 'Podorasje' primary School Renovation. Renovation of the laboratories in the Public Health Institute. Renovation of the Children's Hospital Intensive Care Unit (ICU). Al-Mahra Education and Schools Program. CAT El Salvador- Unidad de Salud Tierra Blanca, San Miguel. Construction of NADMA EOC & DRW - Carriacou, Grenada. Purchase Equipment to Aid in Disaster Relief (Flooding) in Couva/Tabaquite/Talparo Trinidad. HIV Treatment Facility (Annex to Public Hospital) Trujillo. Emergency Helicopter Landing Zones with Night Landing Capability in Zagreb, Karlovac, Osijek and Slavonski Brod. Water Filters - Escuintla. Honduras Disaster Relief Supplies (Kitchen Kits). HA Donation of wheel chairs. COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, School Kits for Turbo, Institucion Educativa Sede Jorge Eliecer Gaitan y sede Gonzalo Mejia.. Renovation/Repair to Kufranjah Comprehensive Health Clinic Addition. SNGRD . Pasto, NARIÑO. Disaster Mitigation and Preparation Equipment, Emergency Operation Center.. MEDCAP - Aquil. Renovation and elevator installation in the inclusive primary school Gjorgjija Pulevski. DRW WAREHOUSE OPERATONS Training & Equipment - Jutiapa, Guatemala. Education Supplies for Ma'an Schools. Vehicle Purchase for Civil Protection and Rescue Service in Podgorica. Parts Replacement for two Southcom Donated Bobcat Skidsteer Loaders - ODM Commonwealth of Dominica. Institutional development for Mexico's National Civil Protection School (Phase I). CMSE PANAMA HIV MEDICAL DONATION. San Marcos de Colon Clinic Renovation. Laos Blood Product Safety Capacity Building. TTO Mayaro/Rio Claro DMU donation of 2 Rescue Boats. Kyiv Neurology Disease Rehab Center for Children Renovation. School Renovation: Escuela Carlos Alberto Rivera Ramos. FY17/18 HA Travel Expenses for Ukraine. Emergency Operations Center Tarapoto, Peru - Disaster Relief Backpack kit donation. Vietnam Site Assessment FY19. Lao American Nutrition Institute - Phase 3. Arturo Mundet Geriatric Center. Disaster Response Warehouse/EOC Training and Equipment for Moquegua. Medical Equipment for 'La Gaviota' Center. Cd. Constitucion Toolkit Backpacks. VP Initiate-HAP MGR-MEDCAP for Narino (Barbacoas) Phase I. COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, Classroom Refurbishment in Riohacha, Comunidad Tocorama. Bahamas Surface Water Rescue Training Refresher Phase 1. Renovation of elementary school in Rozaje. Enhancing Bahamian Firefighting Capability FY18. Four Water Wells for Orocuina, Choluteca. Fiji Oil Spill Response Workshop 2018. COMFORT 2018 Enduring Promise, School Kits for Turbo, Institucion Educativa San Martin de Porras.. Bila, Vitez municipality primary School Renovation. Disaster Management Awareness Program. Sianshand Kindergarten. TUZLA - Orphanage reconstruction. Honduras Disaster Relief Supplies (Hygiene Kits). Bahamas Association for the Physically Disabled School. COLMIL Humanitarian Demining New Platoons Training & Equipping. Yaruca La Ceiba Medcap. CGFM, Estrategica, MEDCAP La Flor. GUAJIRA. Purchase Equipment to Aid in Disaster Relief (Flooding) in Sangre Grande Trinidad. Hancesti Regional Fire and Rescue Station. Medical Equipment for Specialized Hospital in Risan. Far West Blood Bank Facility (Kailali). Busayra Hospital and Jadeed Bagara Clinic Generator. Lupina - Ecofiltro (Water Filters). COL NAV-CGFM, MEDCAP Leguizamo, PUTUMAYO. Physical and Behavioral Health Engagement, JTF Zamboanga. DRW WAREHOUSE OPERATONS Training & Equipment - Retalhuleu, Guatemala. Nicoreni Medium School Sanitation. Disaster Response Warehouse/EOC Training and Equipment for Toledo. Cumming Memorial School. HA Donation - El Platanar, SM. Ayacucho Llochegua School Kits. Tan My Kindergarten. Medical Engagement: San Jose, department of Copan MEDCAP. Starokostyantyniv School Procurements of projectors, computers and TVs. Purchase of four ambulances for the Ministry of Labor, Health, and Social Affairs of Georgia. Kolasin Emergency Room. Renovation of Secondary School 'Luigj Gurakuqi' in Kline. Quweira Primary School Refurbishment. Medicine for emergency kits - Volcano Eruption. Translate DM Course to French, Conduct French Pilot Course, Implement Post-Pilot Changes (Phase 3). Remedial School (Classrooms, Library, Activity Center) for Azraq Refugee Camp Village 5. Medical Engagement: Santa Rosa de Copan MEDCAP. Drochia Preschool # 8 Sanitation. Sava River LiDAR MApping - Croatia. Rescue Boat for city of Carrillo. Clinic (Conchagua, La Union). MEDCAP - Escuintla - Volcano Eruption
